des:
Ask Alexa to open Astrology Trivia
Gather your friends and test you knowledge of astrology. Questions range in difficulty, so anyone can play. The more you play the more you learn. Alexa will explain how the game is played. Are you a super star? Play, have fun, and find out!
Charmed in Company LLP is the oldest mystical metaphysical shoppe in NJ. We created this skill as a fun way to learn about various aspects of astrology. Check out our other skills in the lifestyle, self improvement section.
